  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.2">
<l>vāṇutalim maṭavara lummaik</l>
<l>kāṇumācaiyuṇ ṇaikiṉ ṟāḷviṟal</l>
<l>vāṇaṉāyiran tōṭṭuṇit tīrummaik</l>
<l>kāṇanī rirakka milīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This simple [girl] with a bright forehead</l>
<l>languishes in longing to see you, who are without mercy</l>
<l>in [your] nature, when one sees you who cut off</l>
<l>the thousand shoulders of victorious Bhāṇa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
